{"tid":691783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追求不成狂毆心儀女生　東莞男：從小到大沒得不到的","createTime":"2018-06-06T05:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T07:32:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9e49ece3470249d1a555f2a4f59dcb6568cecadf","tid":691783,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/photo/bkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180606105421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180606%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180606105421&h=92979788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">涉事男子試圖把女事主拖出店外。（網上圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/photo/bkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180606105421\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180606%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180606105421&h=ca893ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">男子用伸縮棍追打馬女。（網上圖片）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n廣東東莞一名馬姓女子早前拒絕了愛慕者的追求後，對方竟於周一（4日）到她工作的地方滋擾，又用伸縮棍威嚇及攻擊馬女及其同事。該名男子更在現場叫囂稱：「從小到大就沒有得不到的東西」，揚言要教訓馬女。<br />\n<br />\n根據店內的閉路電視畫面可見，事發時只有馬姓女事主與一名男同事在店內。涉事男子衝進店內後，情緒激動地要求與馬女單獨對話，雙方因而發生推撞。驚慌之下，馬女跑進櫃台，躲在同事的背後求助。他其後更從袋中取出伸縮棍揮舞，有追打馬女的背部、腿部，甚至拉著其頭部撞牆，並多次掌摑她。<br />\n<br />\n馬女事後表示，自己與該名男子今年1月才認識，隨後他即展開瘋狂追求，「但從始至終，（我）都是拒絕的」。據稱，男子為家中獨子，從小被家人溺愛；在被她拒絕後，他更威脅道：「我現在得不到你，也不會讓你好過。」<br />\n<br />\n而涉事男子亦非首次對女事主施暴，今次更把她打到腦震盪，以及全身軟組織挫傷、耳膜穿孔。警方事後已將涉事男子帶返調查，對其處以行政拘留10天，並罰款500元人民幣（約623港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/bkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180606%2Fbkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001.html&d=vhjfVoIsUf8uppYeFv%2B2IZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=04c71dfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/bkncn-20180606104526318-0606_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8c71fdd97e76383b4b9f7deed7de89a1382f5361","tid":691783,"uid":111872,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"打到腦震盪穿耳膜都係比五舊水又幾撚抵玩"},{"pid":"236ae90101f0f89700099aefd84693f88b842744","tid":691783,"uid":67346,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 警方事後已將涉事男子帶返調查，對其處以行政拘留10天，並罰款500元人民幣（約623港元）</span><br />\n打到人咁都淨係罰坐10日？<br />\n大陸有錢有權真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957d8f493575b8192064ae657fbde09bf0c90890","tid":691783,"uid":116688,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"大把港女鐘意男人夠man"},{"pid":"083ef676c6347691ebc9694d1f868f18f228187c","tid":691783,"uid":62011,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"不要表白，去毆打........"},{"pid":"2f6696bd7aba756622bbe3ae25865d7efe1bb52b","tid":691783,"uid":32051,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:08:31.000Z","msg":"終蟈人就係咁<br />\n以為自己係世界中心"},{"pid":"5c27d937cd77431e014b07ce45d60494a0a76ede","tid":691783,"uid":48277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:10:21.000Z","msg":"千期唔好惹d大陸狗<br />\n<br />\n爛命一條 發起惡上黎殺左你都有份"},{"pid":"db17abb2ade29787595572c159021d40181fa5b0","tid":691783,"uid":78873,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"083ef676c6347691ebc9694d1f868f18f228187c","tid":691783,"uid":62011,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"不要表白，去毆打........"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"人生沒多少時間給你演內心戲..."},{"pid":"a8884e7be60e4ac35c5f0189a6b18fc20f5955ad","tid":691783,"uid":33357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c